{
        "Summary": "This site is a Daybreak Food Vincent Complex located at 3159 BUCHANAN AVE in Eagle Grove, IA and has a state facility ID of 310366393. It is a food production facility, consisting of a layer hen farm, a pullet farm, and an egg-breaking facility. There have been two hazardous material spills at the site, one in 2004 and another in 2016. Previous inspections have found violations of wastewater discharge regulations, including failure to properly dispose of wastewater and failure to maintain adequate records. The site has been issued multiple administrative orders and penalties for these violations. \n\nThe site is also subject to regulation under the Clean Air Act and the Clean Water Act, and has been issued permits under both programs. It is also subject to regulation under the Resource Conservation and Recovery Act (RCRA) and has been issued a permit under that program as well.",
